{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Death is inevitable</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yet, we all have a chance to make things right before the end.<br>Even as time runs out, make use of it wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/title_logo_outline.png?t=1735314066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Graphite is a Roguelike RPG where the player takes part in the fantasy and wonder of a kid's dealing with themes of grief, adulthood and self confidence trougth his very own pen and paper game, using whatever's on hand to bring his dream to fruition.<br><br>Enemies are generated randomly and gain power over time, working together as a team to bring you down.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/Warrior.png?t=1735314066\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/Mage.png?t=1735314066\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/Rogue.png?t=1735314066\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/Tamer.png?t=1735314066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a varied cast of characters, each featuring distinct strategies and personalities to reach as far as you can in this expansive adventure. Each character follows their unique storyline within the larger narrative, interacting with other members of the cast as you make progress.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/windup4.gif?t=1735314066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master the art of timing to achieve victory! Plan your moves strategically and adapt swiftly to counter the enemies' every intention</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/gif_break_prueba.gif?t=1735314066\" />Break your enemies poise to weaken them, but stay vigilant\u2014your own defenses can be broken just as easily!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/event2.gif?t=1735314066\" />Draw adventure cards from the tarot deck that present narrative scenarios with multiple choices affected by your current party composition and progression, serving as a safer alternative to character growth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SHOP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/extras/naipes_gif.gif?t=1735314066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Both you and monsters gain artifacts throughout a run, each one providing unique effects that synergizes with many strategies. Artifacts have no stack limit so you can focus on what you want to specialize their strategy towards.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735314066","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735314066","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/2a3c36dd6e0a146d513db94f37c155606dbdf00c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735314066","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080560/2a3c36dd6e0a146d513db94f37c155606dbdf00c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735314066","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descr